{"tid":2220002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"K11入稟禁手辦民女","createTime":"2020-09-27T10:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T12:10:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5627fa90b725a5eccbdd62a2375b47d3ef8ca4","tid":2220002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/DFICRIEOKRBIBPD3OXNJEFXJYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FDFICRIEOKRBIBPD3OXNJEFXJYY%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=1ef672e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FDFICRIEOKRBIBPD3OXNJEFXJYY%2F&h=d41f1016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/DFICRIEOKRBIBPD3OXNJEFXJYY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nK11入稟禁手辦民女<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】連鎖童裝品牌Chickeeduck繼早前分別被屯門市廣場、荃灣愉景新城及沙田新城市入稟，要求移除商場內分店櫥窗的民主女神像後，再遭另一商場K11 Musea發禁制令，要求移除商場內其分店的小型民主女神像（圖）及抗爭人士公仔等藝術品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/clc1N4S4EIOqT-fgepvJl_xfyWI=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D2N3L4MIYNBKFM2VHVRIDXJ4DQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fclc1N4S4EIOqT-fgepvJl_xfyWI%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD2N3L4MIYNBKFM2VHVRIDXJ4DQ.jpg&h=91134583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四次被逼遷<br />\n<br />\nChickeeduck集團行政總裁周小龍在其facebook專頁上載有關禁制令的相片，表示收到K11 Musea業主要求搬走分店的民主陳列藝術品。Chickeeduck在K11 Musea分店中放置的民主擺設包括數個約10數厘米至約50厘米高的手辦公仔，分別為民主女神像及戴上豬嘴、黃頭盔及眼罩的黑衣抗爭者等。<br />\n<br />\n據《星島日報》報道，K11 Musea商場業主已入稟高等法院要求法庭頒下禁制令，及下令該童裝店移除相關物品，原告為K11 MUSEA的業主HONG KONG ISLAND DEVELOPMENT LIMITED香島發展有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n「只要民主女神一出現，無論（體積）大細都好，就打壓，就要趕走。」。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0bab62756ecd9e4465ab52bf3c8b0c1a68e7a1fb","tid":2220002,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"民女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7849a96ba3d41fb17faac2573bd81bf6194112","tid":2220002,"uid":37528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾商場"},{"pid":"fca1cec919b757abd6228454dfebfd381ad5eb5c","tid":2220002,"uid":242444,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:19:34.000Z","msg":"k11 musea唔會再去<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"87f44d1d36af81f95d422eae0580553aca1ef002","tid":2220002,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd7849a96ba3d41fb17faac2573bd81bf6194112","tid":2220002,"uid":37528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾商場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:19:43.000Z","msg":"燒哂佢"},{"pid":"0ce566d939732436ee6df45e7ce86de911ccebe3","tid":2220002,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾k11"},{"pid":"709cd74e69821c05b0f384d1d4c8a3d02a98ab53","tid":2220002,"uid":119135,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"新世界 x2<br />\n信和 x1<br />\n新鴻基 x1"},{"pid":"772aa079ceb64bd9f3a7abc64eeeda56cc3b0a76","tid":2220002,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"睇錯幫民女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f8cafa653ddbd790f4906c1fd6cc0fa4aeb998","tid":2220002,"uid":45188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"Send 投訴信瘋狂投訴K11"},{"pid":"e8b5bf44f8f0be715f0d240098a8ea0175cbcde5","tid":2220002,"uid":261654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾場唔洗去"},{"pid":"5c2bbcff40fb0ee069a6eff47a24200288a60fb0","tid":2220002,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8b5bf44f8f0be7